  "prompt": "What are some publicly listed solar companies in India?",
  "response": "As of my last update in October 2023, here are some publicly listed solar companies in India:\n\n1. **Tata Power Company Limited**: Tata Power has a significant presence in the renewable energy sector, including solar power generation.\n\n2. **Adani Green Energy Limited**: A part of the Adani Group, this company focuses on large-scale renewable power generation, including solar.\n\n3. **Renew Power Private Limited**: Although it operates as a private company, Renew Power went public through a SPAC merger in 2021 and is listed on the NASDAQ in the United States. \n\n4. **Vikram Solar Limited**: Known for manufacturing solar panels, Vikram Solar has been a key player in the solar energy sector in India.\n\n5. **Solar Industries India Ltd**: While primarily known for explosives, the company has ventured into solar energy solutions.\n\n6. **Inox Wind Limited**: Primarily a wind energy company, Inox has also been active in the solar space through various joint ventures and projects.\n\n7. **Suntech Power Holdings Co., Ltd.**: This solar power company is listed on the New York Stock Exchange and is involved in manufacturing solar panels and providing solar power solutions in various countries, including India.\n\n8. **Waaree Energies Ltd**: Waaree focuses on solar panel manufacturing and has ventured into project development as well.\n\n9. **Jindal Steel and Power Limited**: While predominantly a steel and power company, Jindal Steel has also made investments in renewable energy, including solar.\n\n10. **Hindustan Aeronautics Limited (HAL)**: Although not primarily a solar company, HAL has been involved in solar projects as part of its diversification into renewable energy.\n\nPlease verify the current status of these companies as market conditions and company listings can change.",
